2. Replace body of {project-root}/_memory/validator-sidecar/conversation-context.md (preserve header above first ---): Last session: Pre-save validation of {story_key} ({story_title}). Date: {YYYY-MM-DD}. Findings: {count}. Outcome: {summary}.
If _memory/validator-sidecar/ directory or files don't exist, create them with standard headers (see val-save-session workflow for templates). If writing fails, log warning and continue — memory save is non-blocking.
